data.title: 1997 Porsche 911 GT1 Straßenversion
data.text:
This 1997 Porsche 911 GT1 Straßenversion was recently sold by Girardo & Co. and due to client confidentiality, for this specific car we cannot disclose the details of the car nor the financials of the purchase. At Girardo & Co. we can tailor our service to the clients’ needs, and when necessary we can find cars on behalf of buyers, or offer cars on behalf of sellers privately without the publicity of marketing.

Should you have a similar car that you would like Girardo & Co. to handle discreetly, do not hesitate to contact Max Girardo at max@girardo.com or +44 (0) 20 3621 2923 and we will be happy to give you the best advice to achieve the best result for you.
